{"tid":2179613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仇栩欣案官斥警以大話遮大話, 使用不必要暴力. 白官開左個頭, 我地應該做落去!","createTime":"2020-08-29T08:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T15:02:55.000Z","uid":123774,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8584011f321641ee1f468cbc1f0e479af8784e","tid":2179613,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"唔好用句法治已死就算數<br />\n好多手足仲面對檢控<br />\n被拘留嘅仍然每日面對警暴<br />\n<br />\n都唔好話啲錢留做安家費<br />\n幾時都可以同時進行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【眾籌私人檢控濫暴警】<br />\n<br />\n我的襲警案於8月11日判決，法庭明確指出該警察使用施以不恰當武力，要求將事件紀錄在案。縱雖如此，律政司並未有採取任何行動，彰顯公義。判決之後，有不少市民希望我能夠就事件作出追究，讓濫暴的人能夠正確及公平地被檢控。在尋求法律意見後，我決定向該名警員提出私人檢控，並就相關法律開支進行眾籌。懇請各位香港人仗義相助！<br />\n<br />\n我的眾籌目標為110萬港元（包括眾籌和付款平台收取約10%即約10萬元費用）。在完全支付訴訟和審計有關費用後，餘款將全數捐予612人道支援基金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7%e6%bf%ab%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e7%259c%25be%25e7%25b1%258c%25e7%25a7%2581%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%258e%25a7%25e6%25bf%25ab%25e6%259a%25b4%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2593%25a1%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=d5d6d7b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e7%9c%be%e7%b1%8c%e7%a7%81%e4%ba%ba%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7%e6%bf%ab%e6%9a%b4%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbGbXDH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbGbXDH.png&h=d20b9852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McieaYL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcieaYL.png&h=67c7aede&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f38f2fd299517f0eb1cbd5b6f09793826a9b8791","tid":2179613,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:48:45.000Z","msg":"仇栩欣及助理涉推跌警 警員作供露笑臉遭裁判官嚴厲斥責<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2150991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: